menu "breadboard: bb_storage"

config BB_STORAGE_MAX_BACKENDS
    int "Storage backend registry capacity"
    default 4
    help
        Maximum number of registered backends (e.g. "nvs", "sdcard", "ram")
        in the static registry. Each entry costs sizeof(a name pointer + a
        4-function vtable + a context pointer). Registering more backends
        than this returns BB_ERR_NO_SPACE.

endmenu
